node.text: This is the story of Armenia’s past struggle with the Karabakh conflict, its present courage, and its beautiful future. We are not going anywhere, we will never give up, and may this inspire and motivate you to keep going 🙏 I love and am grateful for all of you ❤️💙🧡🇦🇲 #artsakhstrong #haxteluenq #karabakh #artsakh #armenia

node.title: Armenia’s past struggle with the karabakh conflict
